{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-markdown-post-js","path":"/fluxstore/sign-in/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"siteUrl":"https://docs.inspireui.com","title":"InspireUI Document","description":"InspireUI document"}},"markdownRemark":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Sign In","date":null,"date_pretty":null,"path":null,"meta_title":"FluxStore - Universal mobile commerce Flutter app for Magento, WooCommerce and Opencart","meta_description":"Fluxstore is universal app that fully integration with the Woocommerce, Mangeto and Opencart","image":null,"next":null,"sidebar":"fluxstore","toc":null,"keywords":["fluxstore","flutter app","fluxstore","Magento app","Woo Commerce app","Opencart app"]},"html":"<p>This section shows the way to  configure all Sign In features: SMS, Google, Facebook, Email, Apple; show/ hide Login options, add Forgot Password. Most of these features require Firebase to be set.</p>\n<p>You can do these steps to configure the new App when using any service for Firebase:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Using the <a href=\"http://console.firebase.google.com/?source=post_page---------------------------\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Firebase Console</a>, add an Android app to your project: Follow the assistant, download the generated <code class=\"language-text\">google-services.json</code> file, and place it inside <code class=\"language-text\">android/app</code>.</li>\n<li>Using the <a href=\"http://console.firebase.google.com/?source=post_page---------------------------\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Firebase Console</a>, add an iOS app to your project: Follow the assistant, download the generated <code class=\"language-text\">GoogleService-Info.plist</code> file, open <code class=\"language-text\">ios/Runner.xcworkspace</code> with Xcode, and within Xcode place the file inside <code class=\"language-text\">ios/Runner</code>.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>When installing, if you get issue, please go to <a href=\"https://docs.inspireui.com/fluxstore/common-question/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Common Questions</a> or <a href=\"https://docs.inspireui.com/fluxstore/common-issues/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Common Issues</a> to find the solutions.</p>\n<h2 id=\"1-sms-sign-in\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-sms-sign-in\" aria-label=\"1 sms sign in permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1. SMS Sign In</h2>\n<h4 id=\"11-integrate-with-the-sms-login\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#11-integrate-with-the-sms-login\" aria-label=\"11 integrate with the sms login permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><strong>1.1 Integrate with the SMS Login:</strong></h4>\n<p>Please follow this guide to integrate with the SMS Login. More detailed document, refer to <a href=\"https://pub.dev/packages/firebase_auth\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://pub.dev/packages/firebase_auth</a></p>\n<iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/3NLP-1KX_Vk\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n<p>For android, Open project on firebase console. Then move to Settings/General. You need to upload SHA key to firebase project. You can follow this guide to generate SHA key <a href=\"https://developers.google.com/android/guides/client-auth\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://developers.google.com/android/guides/client-auth</a></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/4e49150d25dbd23f678d49bca7f0f20e/9b270/sha_firebase.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 41%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Packages_get\"\n        title=\"Packages_get\"\n        src=\"/static/4e49150d25dbd23f678d49bca7f0f20e/29d74/sha_firebase.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/4e49150d25dbd23f678d49bca7f0f20e/b4ec0/sha_firebase.png 200w,\n/static/4e49150d25dbd23f678d49bca7f0f20e/24144/sha_firebase.png 400w,\n/static/4e49150d25dbd23f678d49bca7f0f20e/29d74/sha_firebase.png 800w,\n/static/4e49150d25dbd23f678d49bca7f0f20e/5c837/sha_firebase.png 1200w,\n/static/4e49150d25dbd23f678d49bca7f0f20e/9b270/sha_firebase.png 1280w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>In case you meet this issue: after creating APK and releasing the app in App Stores, you get error when login with SMS Login. You need to go to the App stores and copy the SHA-1 key and past to your Firebase setting:</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/3273a1380e757f91034ae6a8726351d5/45bf3/smslogin1.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 52.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"FDK path\"\n        title=\"FDK path\"\n        src=\"/static/3273a1380e757f91034ae6a8726351d5/93d59/smslogin1.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/3273a1380e757f91034ae6a8726351d5/7a70a/smslogin1.jpg 200w,\n/static/3273a1380e757f91034ae6a8726351d5/b2cea/smslogin1.jpg 400w,\n/static/3273a1380e757f91034ae6a8726351d5/93d59/smslogin1.jpg 800w,\n/static/3273a1380e757f91034ae6a8726351d5/0516a/smslogin1.jpg 1200w,\n/static/3273a1380e757f91034ae6a8726351d5/43ad0/smslogin1.jpg 1600w,\n/static/3273a1380e757f91034ae6a8726351d5/45bf3/smslogin1.jpg 1920w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/e9fce2fc10674cda0f203bfa8bc8a87d/45bf3/smslogin2.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 52.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"FDK path\"\n        title=\"FDK path\"\n        src=\"/static/e9fce2fc10674cda0f203bfa8bc8a87d/93d59/smslogin2.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/e9fce2fc10674cda0f203bfa8bc8a87d/7a70a/smslogin2.jpg 200w,\n/static/e9fce2fc10674cda0f203bfa8bc8a87d/b2cea/smslogin2.jpg 400w,\n/static/e9fce2fc10674cda0f203bfa8bc8a87d/93d59/smslogin2.jpg 800w,\n/static/e9fce2fc10674cda0f203bfa8bc8a87d/0516a/smslogin2.jpg 1200w,\n/static/e9fce2fc10674cda0f203bfa8bc8a87d/43ad0/smslogin2.jpg 1600w,\n/static/e9fce2fc10674cda0f203bfa8bc8a87d/45bf3/smslogin2.jpg 1920w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h4 id=\"32-change-sms-default-country\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#32-change-sms-default-country\" aria-label=\"32 change sms default country permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><strong>3.2 Change SMS default country:</strong></h4>\n<p>Open <code class=\"language-text\">lib/screens/login_sms/login_sms_constants.dart</code> and change the default country: (if not found, please check <code class=\"language-text\">lib/common/constants/general.dart</code>)</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"dart\"><pre class=\"language-dart\"><code class=\"language-dart\"><span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">LoginSMSConstants</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">static</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> String countryCodeDefault <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'VN'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">static</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> String dialCodeDefault <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'+84'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">static</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> String nameDefault <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'Vietnam'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>countryCodeDefault</strong>: default country IOS Code.</li>\n<li><strong>dialCodeDefault</strong>: default country phone IOS Code when login as SMS Login feature.</li>\n<li><strong>nameDefault</strong>: default name of country.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"2-google-sign-in\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-google-sign-in\" aria-label=\"2 google sign in permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2. Google Sign In</h2>\n<p>We have added this library <a href=\"https://pub.dev/packages/google_sign_in\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><code class=\"language-text\">google_sign_in</code></a> from pub.dev and upgrade new <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/mstore-api\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><code class=\"language-text\">mstore-api</code></a> plugin to support for this feature, you need to update Firebase setting to activate this feature from the app (also make sure update the google-service file to Fluxstore project).</p>\n<p>Please check <a href=\"https://medium.com/@inspireui/setup-google-login-for-flutter-apps-fedc58a490b8\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">the manual guide</a> for the detailed steps.</p>\n<p><strong>Video guide:</strong></p>\n<iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/14ALBSwvV4E\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n<h2 id=\"3-facebook-sign-in\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#3-facebook-sign-in\" aria-label=\"3 facebook sign in permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>3. Facebook Sign In</h2>\n<p>This part shows the way to set up Facebook login on your Flutter application. This needs to use the <a href=\"https://pub.dev/packages/flutter_facebook_login\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">FlutterFacebookLogin package</a>  </p>\n<p>Please check <a href=\"https://medium.com/@inspireui/setup-facebook-login-for-flutter-apps-4e7bd031479d\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">the manual guide</a> for the detailed steps.</p>\n<p><strong>Video guide:</strong></p>\n<iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/14ALBSwvV4E\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n<h2 id=\"4-apple-sign-in\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#4-apple-sign-in\" aria-label=\"4 apple sign in permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>4. Apple Sign In</h2>\n<span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/7c5e8314271380fa81e27890c9622d1a/f66ae/apple_signin_fluxstore_flutter_inspireui.png\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 172.99999999999997%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/png;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"FDK path\" title=\"FDK path\" src=\"/static/7c5e8314271380fa81e27890c9622d1a/29d74/apple_signin_fluxstore_flutter_inspireui.png\" srcset=\"/static/7c5e8314271380fa81e27890c9622d1a/b4ec0/apple_signin_fluxstore_flutter_inspireui.png 200w,\n/static/7c5e8314271380fa81e27890c9622d1a/24144/apple_signin_fluxstore_flutter_inspireui.png 400w,\n/static/7c5e8314271380fa81e27890c9622d1a/29d74/apple_signin_fluxstore_flutter_inspireui.png 800w,\n/static/7c5e8314271380fa81e27890c9622d1a/f66ae/apple_signin_fluxstore_flutter_inspireui.png 930w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\">\n  </a>\n    </span>\n<p>If your app using third-party login service, it will require to use Apple Sign In to get approval from Apple. To enable this features on Fluxstore please make sure following config:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Enable the <a href=\"#5-showhide-the-login-options\">config section</a> to enable Apple Sign In (the default is active).</li>\n<li>Enable the the Apple Login option on Firebase - <a href=\"https://tppr.me/yd1Yv\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://tppr.me/yd1Yv</a> - this option is used to register Apple user account with the Firebase app.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Important Note: </p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Apple Sign In is only available for device with iOS 13 and up</strong> (not work with the <strong>iOS Simulator</strong>): you might need to open Xcode to make sure you have enable Sign in with Apple in capabilities in <code class=\"language-text\">Runner</code> target of <code class=\"language-text\">ios/Runner.xcworkspace</code>.</li>\n</ul>\n<span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/5896d327b2aa0b9af6c1df90a6463d45/fc664/sign-in-with-apple-capability.png\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 66%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/png;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"FDK path\" title=\"FDK path\" src=\"/static/5896d327b2aa0b9af6c1df90a6463d45/29d74/sign-in-with-apple-capability.png\" srcset=\"/static/5896d327b2aa0b9af6c1df90a6463d45/b4ec0/sign-in-with-apple-capability.png 200w,\n/static/5896d327b2aa0b9af6c1df90a6463d45/24144/sign-in-with-apple-capability.png 400w,\n/static/5896d327b2aa0b9af6c1df90a6463d45/29d74/sign-in-with-apple-capability.png 800w,\n/static/5896d327b2aa0b9af6c1df90a6463d45/5c837/sign-in-with-apple-capability.png 1200w,\n/static/5896d327b2aa0b9af6c1df90a6463d45/db573/sign-in-with-apple-capability.png 1600w,\n/static/5896d327b2aa0b9af6c1df90a6463d45/fc664/sign-in-with-apple-capability.png 2310w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\">\n  </a>\n    </span>\n<p><em>If Sign in with Apple capability is not enabled, please enable it. You can follow this guide on <a href=\"https://developer.apple.com/documentation/xcode/adding_capabilities_to_your_app\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">adding capabilities to your app</a>.</em></p>\n<ul>\n<li>üêûBug Login: <strong>revoke the account access on your iOS device if could not login on Fluxstore</strong>, by opening the <code class=\"language-text\">Setting</code> on iOS in your iPhone and tap on your name at the top, press <code class=\"language-text\">Password &amp; Security</code>, then you could see list the <code class=\"language-text\">Apps that using Apple ID</code>,  you can <code class=\"language-text\">delete</code> any of them to <code class=\"language-text\">revoke</code> access</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"5-showhide-the-login-options\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#5-showhide-the-login-options\" aria-label=\"5 showhide the login options permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>5. Show/hide the Login options</h2>\n<p>Update the <code class=\"language-text\">lib/common/config/general.dart</code> to show/hide the Login options:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"dart\"><pre class=\"language-dart\"><code class=\"language-dart\"><span class=\"token comment\">/// Option to show/hide the Social Login</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> kLoginSetting <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token string\">\"IsRequiredLogin\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">false</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token string\">'showAppleLogin'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token string\">'showFacebook'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token string\">'showSMSLogin'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token string\">'showGoogleLogin'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">/// Enable the Start Rating features</span>\n<span class=\"token string\">\"EnableRating\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">/// If the Start Rating is empty, we could hide it or keep with blank star</span>\n<span class=\"token string\">\"hideEmptyProductListRating\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">false</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">/// set to true if you have finish running Re-generate image plugin</span>\n<span class=\"token string\">\"kIsResizeImage\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">false</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><strong>File lib/common/config/general.dart:</strong></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/5529f36de79de3ca39bd7a54bd6f0160/582e9/0_4.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 44.99999999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"fluxstore-1\"\n        title=\"fluxstore-1\"\n        src=\"/static/5529f36de79de3ca39bd7a54bd6f0160/29d74/0_4.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/5529f36de79de3ca39bd7a54bd6f0160/b4ec0/0_4.png 200w,\n/static/5529f36de79de3ca39bd7a54bd6f0160/24144/0_4.png 400w,\n/static/5529f36de79de3ca39bd7a54bd6f0160/29d74/0_4.png 800w,\n/static/5529f36de79de3ca39bd7a54bd6f0160/5c837/0_4.png 1200w,\n/static/5529f36de79de3ca39bd7a54bd6f0160/582e9/0_4.png 1400w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h2 id=\"6-add-forgot-password\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#6-add-forgot-password\" aria-label=\"6 add forgot password permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>6. <strong>Add Forgot password</strong></h2>\n<p>This native forgot password feature is available for the WooCommerce only. To enable the <strong>Native forgot password screen</strong>, we just only set <code class=\"language-text\">forgetPassword: &quot;&quot;</code> in the <code class=\"language-text\">lib/common/config.dart</code>. Otherwise, using the external Forgot password URL to open the screen as the Webview screen.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"json\"><pre class=\"language-json\"><code class=\"language-json\"><span class=\"token comment\">/// set blank to use as native screen</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">\"forgetPassword\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"http://demo.mstore.io/wp-login.php?action=lostpassword\"</span></code></pre></div>","fields":{"slug":"/fluxstore/sign-in/"},"timeToRead":5,"excerpt":"This section shows the way to  configure all Sign In features: SMS, Google, Facebook, Email, Apple; show/ hide Login options, add Forgot‚Ä¶","fileAbsolutePath":"/Users/minh/Data/Projects/web/inspireui-document/content/fluxstore/sign-in.md"}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/fluxstore/sign-in/"}},"staticQueryHashes":[]}